Text.string: Behold, my beautiful drones! They're gonna make you sad!
This is me right now! ... And this is gonna be YOU!
Heh-heh, smiley face! 'Cause you're gonna be DEAD face!
I'm gonna make this hurt! A loooot!
Just so you know. We're all laughing at you! (laugh)
Introducing the MVP! All my drones!
All power to the drone squad!
Drone party! AND YOU'RE NOT INVITED!
Dance, my drones! Dance for me!
[humming to animation] Ooh, yeah, ooh, yeah, uhn-uhn-uhn-uhn-uhn, UHN! Yeah!
Killing you's gonna be super easy!
Your death in a minute or less!
I see all your moves in advance!
You'll be dead before you know it!
We got a gunner to frag!
A new soldier enters the arena!
Hey, soldier girl, let's go to war!
We've got more guns than you!
She got guns. We got guns. Let's do this!
Don't let him out of your sights!
Where do you think you're going?
Someone scan that guy's gear for me!
A Siren. This just got interesting!
[sarcastic] We're sooo scared of the Siren!
Keep an eye out for critters!
Knew you couldn't handle the game!
I know what you're thinking! Run, run!
I'm gonna use you for an ottoman!
No one will come to your funeral!
Carry the one, two plus two is three!
I see the problem now! Not enough fractions!
You look a mess. Stop it!
Where the hell is the changelog?!
Don't shoot my drones, you morons!
Get too close and I'll kill you too!
You think you're cool or something?
I see your birds and raise you a drone squad!
Am I supposed to be scared?
Ooh, I'm gonna steal that design!
You didn't make that, did you?
Is there a patent for that yet?
I cloned myself once. Bad idea.
Yeah, you WISH there were two of me!
But which one is the real one?!
Let me stick a cord in you!
What level do I get THAT skill?!
Two can play at that game!
Brought a bot to a drone fight!
They'll have to come out eventually!
I will beat them by myself!
Hope you've got a health potion!
Don't poop, it'll only slow my looting down!
What are you trying to prove?
Would you check out that K-D-R? [“kill-death ratio”]
Got our work cut out for us!
I will return and destroy you!
Mashing buttons! (beat) What?! IT'S A STRATEGY.
I'm supposed to be the A-D Carry!
Can't afford to lose the DPS!
I'm the friggin' beeeest! ... And you're dead!
Good times for me! ... Bad times for you!
I got you, noob! ... Now just die already!
At first I was like... but then I LOL'd!
Down for the count! Ha, ha, ha, ha!
You mad? Cause I'm LOL'ing so hard right now!
My K-D-A just went up! Thanks!
[singsong] Dead meat, smell my feet, give me someone's ass to beat.
And a-one, and a-two, and you're gonna die!
Call me maestro, conductor of death and destruction!
Guess who just snuffed you out! Go on! Guess!
Ohhhh! Hail to the champ! By the way, I'M the champ!
This! This is the face of your DESTRUCTION!
Don't say I never did nothin' for ya!
Too heavy to carry, need allies!
Can't do this alone out here!
We're running low on guys here!
Good to have you on the team!
This dance cost me ten dollars!
Dancin' on your grave! You suck!
What's that smell? Smells like victory!
Huh? What? Oh! You got wrecked!
What's that?! Just me! Kicking YOUR ASS!
Look at that! You got SPANKED!
We're gonna wreck you SO HARD!
Oh god, blood. Save me, you fools!
If I die, all hope's lost.
You made me bleed my own blood!
You're so dead if I die!
There a doctor in the house?
Gonna hover on your grave, loser!
I'm the one who got ya!
This epic mount's a rip off!
Just so you know, this is the guy that's gonna kill youuu! (laugh)
Hey, hey! This NOG best NOG!
This arrow points to YOUR DOOM!
